  <summary date="2021-02-18T19:35:33Z" status="Introduced in House">Require USCP to Utilize Body-Worn Cameras Act

This bill requires each uniformed officer of the U.S. Capitol Police whose job duties include interacting with the general public to use a body-worn camera and ensure it is activated while on duty. This requirement does not apply to an officer serving on a personal protection detail.</summary>
